1
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:02,840
(DOCTOR WHO THEME)

2
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,560
AVERY: April the 1st, 1699.

3
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,880
The good ship Fancy.

4
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:15,400
Captain's journal.

5
00:00:16,240 --> 00:00:18,520
Eight days we've been
stranded in these waters

6
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:21,080
and still there is no wind
to fill our sails.

7
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,480
The ship is helpless,

8
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:26,000
marooned in a silent ocean.

9
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,560
We cannot run and we cannot fight.

10
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,760
All we can do is await our fate.

11
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,880
An enemy lurks out there
in the darkness.

12
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,200
She comes for us
when the ocean is still.

13
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:43,720
One by one, the crew have been taken.

14
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:48,000
The men are exhausted with fear.

15
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:51,120
We cannot last much longer.

16
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:57,080
I feel an evil presence
lurking in the shadows somewhere,

17
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,720
forever watching me.

18
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:05,880
I pray for a fair wind that will
carry us away from this accursed place,

19
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:12,360
but I fear that we are all doomed
to die here.

